9 6–237.
10 WHEN A DEFENDANT IS CONVICTED OF OR PLEADS GUILTY TO A CRIME AND IS
11 SENTENCED TO A TERM OF IMPRISONMENT OF AT LEAST 6 MONTHS BUT NOT MORE
